                    },
                    "body": "There are many of these types of errors in the docblocks of Zend Framework.  According to [the manual page|http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/manual\/en\/zend.db.statement.html#zend.db.statement.fetching.fetch] {{Zend_Db_Statement::fetch}} should return FALSE if no records are found, so {{Zend_Db_Adapter::fetchRow}} is functioning as intended.\r\n\r\nFor this case I will correct the docblock",
